This artifact wires the "tdd-guard" PreToolUse hook from nizos/tdd-guard.

No source code is vendored — Patronus only reproduces the hook registration
(event, matcher, and command) documented in the upstream manual-install guide
(docs/installation.md) so the agent's settings invoke the `tdd-guard` binary.
That binary is delivered by the sibling `tdd-guard` recipe (deliver: npm), so
this hook and that recipe install together via the `core` profile.

Patronus wires only the enforcement PreToolUse hook (matcher
Write|Edit|MultiEdit|TodoWrite). The upstream's optional UserPromptSubmit and
SessionStart context-feeder hooks are intentionally not wired.

